snippet.title: Death: The Ascension - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Death: The Ascension Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1371220?utm_source=Youtube_Triler

Play a card game that actually a resource management game.
While you try not to die by the hands of death.
And save your wife, while you try not to die.
And gamble everything you already have.
